data.description: Come see this two-bedroom two baths conventional-style home in the  Gramercy Park section of Los Angeles. The nice curb appeal that reflects the owner's pride will greet you the minute you pull up to the home. Hardwood floor throughout the home with a painted interior that makes it light and airy. There is a nice size den with a decorative fireplace. The bedrooms are spacious with a nice size window that brings in a lot of natural sunlight and fresh air. Laundry hook-up inside the home eliminates the need to go to any public laundry mat. There is an enclosed patio in the back of the home for additional relaxation. There is a bonus single unit which includes a kitchenette, and a bathroom in the backyard which can be used for whatever the buyer sees fit. The backyard is spacious and perfect for social events with friends or family. This property is centrally located in Los Angeles close to the newly built So-Fi stadium, Clipper’s Basketball Arena, and minutes from downtown Los Angeles.
